item.title: TME
item.description: score:174 Chances: Tencent Music Entertainment Group has renewed a multi-year strategic licensing agreement with Universal Music Group, indicating a strong commitment to creating value for artists and exceptional experiences for music lovers. The company has a leading position in the online music and audio entertainment platform in China, with a strong portfolio of product brands including QQ Music, Kugou Music, Kuwo Music, and WeSing.
